Project AMI - Team TheParents

This is where any unused or failed code will be placed.

Most of the code here will be from the potential prototype of AMI or code from the peer-reviews.

Please ensure it is documented before committing here of who wrote the code and who is committing the code to this directory. If it doesn't already exist, please add a brief comment of why the code ended up here.

This will help if we need to rollback or can reutilize any code that ends up here.
